    <chapter>
      <heading>
        Software documentation for the TTIOFeature class
      </heading>
      <class name="TTIOFeature" super="NSObject">
        <declared>TTIOFeature.h</declared>
        <conform>NSCopying</conform>
        <desc>
          A feature-level observation: a peak detected in one run,
          with retention time + m/z + charge + per-sample
          abundances. Sits between {@link
          TTIOIdentification} (spectrum-level) and
          {@link TTIOQuantification} (entity-level): the
          row-level record required by mzTab's PEP section
          (peptide-level quantification in the 1.0
          proteomics dialect) and by mzTab-M's SMF/SME
          sections (small-molecule feature + evidence in the
          2.0.0-M metabolomics dialect). API status:
          Provisional (v0.12.0 M78). Cross-language
          equivalents: Python: ttio.feature.Feature Java:
          com.dtwthalion.ttio.Feature
        </desc>
        <method type="instancetype" factory="yes">
          <sel>featureWithId:</sel>
